RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select a.contract_ref_no, a.contract_ccy, a.counterparty, b.customer_name1, a.user_defined_status, a.department_code, a.branch, a.treasury_source from oltbs_contract a, oltms_customer b where a.branch = global.current_branch and a.module_code = 'LB' and a.contract_status in ('A', 'L') and b.customer_no = a.counterparty order by a.contract_ref_no

select distinct contract_ref_no from oltbs_contract_liq where contracT_ref_no in (select contract_ref_no from oltbs_contract where branch = global.current_branch and module_code = 'LB' and contract_status in ('A', 'L'))

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: Branch IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVW_USER_BRANCHES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID INTERSECT SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMTB_USER_ROLE WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVWS_USER_CENTRAL_ROLES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT TO_CHAR(DUE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') DUE_DATE FROM OLTBS_AMOUNT_DUE A WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND INFLOW_OUTFLOW = CASE WHEN COMPONENT ='PRINCIPAL' THEN 'I' ELSE INFLOW_OUTFLOW END AND (NVL(AMOUNT_DUE, 0) -(NVL(AMOUNT_SETTLED, 0) + NVL(ADJUSTED_AMOUNT, 0))) > 0 AND 'Y' <> (SELECT Olpks_Servicesy.Fn_Is_Ristourne_Component(a.COMPONENT, ?) FROM DUAL) ORDER BY DUE_DATE
SELECT distinct A.CPTY,A.CUST_NAME FROM LBVW_PYMNT_SMRY A ORDER BY A.CPTY
